<main class="flex-grow py-8 md:py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-8 text-center md:text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">수거 신청</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">편리한 무료 택배 수거를 위해 픽업 정보를 입력해주세요.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8">
            <div class="flex-grow lg:w-2/3">
                
                <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 overflow-hidden mb-6">
                    <div class="p-6 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
                        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary text-white text-xs">4</span>
                            수거 및 정산 정보 입력
                        </h2>
                        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 ml-8">기사님 방문을 위해 정확한 주소와 연락처를 입력해주세요.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 space-y-8">
                        <!-- Applicant Info -->
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="material-icons text-base">person</span>
                                신청자 정보
                            </h3>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-4">
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">성함</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="input-name" placeholder="이름을 입력하세요" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">휴대전화번호</label>
                                    <input type="tel" id="input-phone" placeholder="010-0000-0000" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">주소</label>
                                <div class="flex gap-2">
                                    <input type="text" id="input-address" placeholder="주소를 검색해주세요" class="flex-grow px-4 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white" readonly>
                                    <button onclick="alert('주소 검색 기능은 데모입니다.')" class="bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">우편번호 검색</button>
                                </div>
                                <input type="text" id="input-address-detail" placeholder="상세주소를 입력해주세요 (동, 호수 등)" class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Collection Schedule & Location -->
                        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
                            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="material-icons text-base">schedule</span>
                                수거 일정 및 장소
                            </h3>
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">방문 희망일</label>
                                    <div class="relative">
                                        <input type="date" id="input-date" class="w-full pl-4 pr-10 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                                        <!-- Calendar icon is native in input type date, but can add custom overlay if needed. Keeping native for simplicity. -->
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2">방문 시간</label>
                                    <div class="relative">
                                        <select id="input-time" class="w-full pl-4 pr-10 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary appearance-none transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                                            <option disabled selected>시간 선택</option>
                                            <option>오전 (09:00 ~ 12:00)</option>
                                            <option>오후 (13:00 ~ 18:00)</option>
                                        </select>
                                        <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 flex items-center px-2 pointer-events-none text-gray-500">
                                            <span class="material-icons">expand_more</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">수거 장소 (물품 보관 위치)</label>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
                                    <button onclick="selectLocation(this, '문 앞')" class="location-btn px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all">문 앞</button>
                                    <button onclick="selectLocation(this, '경비실')" class="location-btn px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all">경비실</button>
                                    <button onclick="selectLocation(this, '택배함')" class="location-btn px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all">택배함</button>
                                    <button onclick="selectLocation(this, '직접 전달')" class="location-btn px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary transition-all">직접 전달</button>
                                </div>
                                <input type="text" id="input-memo" placeholder="공동현관 비밀번호 등 기사님께 전달할 메모를 입력해주세요." class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Settlement Account Info -->
                        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
                            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="material-icons text-base">account_balance</span>
                                정산 계좌 정보
                            </h3>
                            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
                                <div class="md:w-1/3 relative">
                                    <select id="input-bank" class="w-full pl-4 pr-10 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary appearance-none transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                                        <option disabled selected>은행 선택</option>
                                        <option>국민은행</option>
                                        <option>신한은행</option>
                                        <option>우리은행</option>
                                        <option>하나은행</option>
                                        <option>농협</option>
                                        <option>카카오뱅크</option>
                                        <option>토스뱅크</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 flex items-center px-2 pointer-events-none text-gray-500">
                                        <span class="material-icons">expand_more</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <input type="text" id="input-account" placeholder="계좌번호 (-없이 입력)" class="flex-grow px-4 py-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 focus:border-primary transition-shadow text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2 flex items-center gap-1">
                                <span class="material-icons text-sm">info</span>
                                예금주명은 신청자 성함과 일치해야 합니다.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Navigation Buttons -->
                    <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900/50 px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
                        <button onclick="history.back()" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors">
                            <span class="material-icons text-base">arrow_back</span>
                            이전 단계
                        </button>
                        <button onclick="submitRequest()" class="bg-primary hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/30 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 flex items-center gap-2">
                            수거 신청 완료
                            <span class="material-icons text-sm">check_circle</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Sidebar -->
            <div class="lg:w-1/3">
                <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 overflow-hidden relative">
                        <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-blue-400"></div>
                        <div class="p-6">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="material-icons text-primary">receipt_long</span>
                                매입 신청 요약
                            </h3>
                            <div id="single-summary" class="space-y-4 mb-6 text-sm">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-start pb-3 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 border-dashed">
                                    <span class="text-gray-500">기기 종류</span>
                                    <span id="summary-device" class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-right">노트북</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-start pb-3 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 border-dashed">
                                    <span class="text-gray-500">제조사</span>
                                    <span id="summary-manufacturer" class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-right">삼성전자 (Samsung)</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-start pb-3 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 border-dashed">
                                    <span class="text-gray-500">모델명</span>
                                    <span id="summary-model" class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-right">Samsung Galaxy Book 3 Pro</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-start pb-3 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 border-dashed">
                                    <span class="text-gray-500">주요 사양</span>
                                    <div class="text-right">
                                        <div id="summary-cpu" class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Intel Core i5</div>
                                        <div id="summary-memory" class="text-xs text-gray-500">16GB RAM / 512GB SSD</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                                    <span class="text-gray-500">기기 상태</span>
                                    <span id="summary-condition" class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800 dark:bg-green-900 dark:text-green-200">
                                        A급 (정상)
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div id="multi-summary" class="mb-4 hidden">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                                    <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">추가된 기기</span>
                                    <span id="multi-count" class="text-xs text-gray-500">0대</span>
                                </div>
                                <div id="multi-list" class="space-y-2 max-h-48 overflow-auto"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-primary/5 dark:bg-gray-700/50 rounded-xl p-5 text-center border border-primary/10 mb-4">
                                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-1">최종 예상 매입가</p>
                                <div id="summary-price" class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary tracking-tight">
                                    ₩ 650,000
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">* 실물 검수 후 최종 확정됩니다.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700 p-5">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 p-2 rounded-full text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">
                                <span class="material-icons">security</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-gray-900 dark:text-white">데이터 영구 삭제 보장</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1 leading-relaxed">블랑코(Blancco) 솔루션을 사용하여 개인정보를 100% 영구 삭제 후 인증서를 발급해 드립니다.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 p-2 rounded-full text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">
                                <span class="material-icons">local_shipping</span>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-sm text-gray-900 dark:text-white">무료 수거 서비스</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1 leading-relaxed">신청 완료 후 지정 택배사가 방문하여 무료로 기기를 수거합니다.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">신청 과정이 어려우신가요?</p>
                        <a class="text-sm font-medium text-primary hover:underline" href="#">고객센터 문의하기 (1588-0000)</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>